Pacad Inc said it has enteredinto a contractual agreement with &lt;Okamoto U.S.A. Inc> tomarket condoms manufactured by Okamoto's parent company,Okamoto Riken Gomu Co Ltd of Japan.    Pacad president David Tucker said the agreement covered theentire U.S. and Caribbean.    "With mounting public health concerns we expect our condomsales to begin within 30 days and grow rapidly in 1987," Tuckersaid. "We find perception of quality and value in Japaneseproducts is just now crossing over from cars and cameras tocondoms." Reuter&#3;